# Marketing Content

Place marketing campaigns, copy, and strategies here.

## File Naming Convention

- `campaign-name.md` - Campaign details
- `copy-platform-date.md` - Marketing copy
- `strategy-topic.md` - Marketing strategies

## Example Structure

```markdown
# Campaign Name

## Objective
What we want to achieve

## Target Audience
Who we're targeting

## Channels
- Social media
- Email
- Ads

## Timeline
Start and end dates

## Budget
Budget allocation

## KPIs
Success metrics
```
